1 <html [1]> <html [1]>
2 <html [1]> <html [1]>
3 <html [1]> <html [1]>
4 <html [1]> <html [1]>
```
:::
:::


Now we create the table by calling the gt() command.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(gt)

education %>% 
    gt()
```

